# Routines

- On start, the daemon should read the configuration file and start all programs marked as "autostart" automatically.

- Implement the supervisor state flow:

STOPPED → STARTING → RUNNING → EXITED  (exit attendu)
                   ↘ BACKOFF            (mort pendant starttime)
                              ↘ FATAL   (trop de retries)
          RUNNING  → STOPPING → STOPPED (stop manuel)